posts.post_title: WTB:  T206 Midgrade Want List  (Stars & Commons)
posts.post_content:
Really been enjoying getting back into the T206 set recently, after a bit of time away focusing on other projects.
I have around 100 graded T206's from PSA 4 - 6 (some SGC's), and would love to knock a few more off the long-term wishlist.  

Looking for cards graded PSA/SGC 4.0 - 5.5.  Centering is the most important factor overall.  
PayPal F&F funds are at the ready.

Two great deals with solid Net54'ers done already has put a nice dent in the wishlist.

Still looking for the cards listed.  Email any pics to the above address.  Thank you!
